						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Āñjanēya temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1480, Kāḷayukti, Māgha, śu. 7,</hi> corresponding to 1559 A.D., January 16, Monday.</p>						

						<p>It records the gift of land at Uḷachala as Bhaṭamānya by <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Māḍrāju-Narasarājayyadēva Mahārāju to Bhaṭṭu Tippayya.</p>						

						</summary>
